isNameMigrated(bytes32).details: returns whether the label name is migrated or not, the input is label name without .bnb suffix

isNameOwner(address,bytes32).details: returns whether the label name is migrated or not, the input is label name without .bnb suffix

migratedDuration(uint256).details: calculate the duration of migrated domains, domains in grace period  cannot be migrated

nodeHashByLabel(string).details: returns the full name hash, if the labelname.bnb, the input is label name without .bnb suffix

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

start.details: only in the period of [start, end], the discount is enabled
